Terrorists: FIGHT OFF THE INFIDELS, WHEN VICTORY LOOKS GRIM, PRESS E TO TAKE THEM WITH YOU! Counter-Terrorists: Don't get blowed up.

This map took me a while to make, and a tons of work by myself and others to get this to work smoothly. But we finally did it. CT's kill the T's, T's kill the CT's, and when things aren't happening your way, take the fuckers with you and hit E to suicide bomb!
